property.value:
local delay = 2000 -- every 2000ms = 2s local last = 0 local pingrec = 0
function update() local now = getMillis() if(now - last > delay) then if(pingrec == 0) then self.properties.color.r = 1 self.properties.color.g = 0 self.properties.color.b = 0 self.properties.color.a = 0.5 print(self.color) end last = now pingrec = 0 sendOSC('/GrandMA3/cmd', 'sendosc 1 "/ping,s,00ff007f"') end end
function onReceiveOSC() pingrec = 1 end

local savename = "" local helper = ""
function onValueChanged(key) print(self.values.text) if self.values.text == "127" then savename = savename:sub(1, -2) self.values.text = savename elseif self.values.text == "1000" then savename = "" self.values.text = savename elseif self.values.text == "1001" then helper = " Thru " self.values.text = savename .. helper savename = self.values.text elseif self.values.text == "1002" then helper = " At " self.values.text = savename .. helper savename = self.values.text elseif self.values.text == "1003" then helper = " Full " self.values.text = savename .. helper savename = self.values.text elseif self.values.text == "1111" then sendOSC('/GrandMA3/cmd', savename) sendOSC('/GrandMA3/cmd', "call Plugin TouchOSCSel") else self.values.text = savename .. string.char(self.values.text) savename = self.values.text end end
